{"tid":1555453,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日問太子站黃衫借廁所 竟然唔撚識","createTime":"2019-09-09T11:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T10:06:50.000Z","uid":227275,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fd59595742155016976bb60359c4e78a48db56d9","tid":1555453,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:00:07.000Z","msg":"有2條好撚正既黃衫妹 認真係好撚正<br />\n問佢地借廁所 佢地唔明 走左去問隔離2個黃衫男人 <br />\n之後佢地4個討論左10幾秒就同我講無得借 <br />\n叫我去附近商場<br />\n<br />\n屌比太子果頭邊有商場架<br />\n始創都計? 仲要唔撚識答 <br />\n好撚鬼 但2條女唔似差婆 2個都啡色長髮靚女樣<br />\n<br />\n到底咩人黎 果2個黃衫男身型都唔似係狗<br />\n再隔離又有2個粉紅衫 一個似學生一個似師奶<br />\n<br />\n總共6個人 分2人一組企埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部唔似狗 但唔知係度做乜既"},{"pid":"bb441039fe4846c43f1db30b663f235de326af42","tid":1555453,"uid":198402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:02:44.000Z","msg":"點解始創唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"027b3140e88c802c3b1b0a9db87971f3eff0662f","tid":1555453,"uid":117276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:05:12.000Z","msg":"即場瀨俾佢睇"},{"pid":"3a3cf20b2e84fddaaf2167cf5598771da60cadab","tid":1555453,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb441039fe4846c43f1db30b663f235de326af42","tid":1555453,"uid":198402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:02:44.000Z","msg":"點解始創唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:34:43.000Z","msg":"咁撚遠都計?"},{"pid":"a88073323df8c6f5d3db5e8851d94ae5d865f8f0","tid":1555453,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"027b3140e88c802c3b1b0a9db87971f3eff0662f","tid":1555453,"uid":117276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:05:12.000Z","msg":"即場瀨俾佢睇"},"citedBy":1,"r